race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Handicap
race.comment: BOSSED UP (5) loves this sprint journey with two wins and four placings from just seven attempts and will be cherry-ripe now third-up from the spell. Gets Maloney back on top from a low draw and will be right there at the business end. BARBERRY SPUR (16) got the maiden out of the way at Doomben before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Looks the runner in this field with the most upside and can make his presence felt while fresh. SPEEDY ONE (4) is a three-time winner over this trip and will be at peak fitness for this. Top-three credentials on best form. BREMEL (10) brings NSW formlines to the table and should be kept very safe. MOULIN MISS (9) makes some appeal while fresh.
